      "x": 710,
      "y": 210,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "🛑 Gate A: Design & Plan Gate\n\n[Audit]: Human review AI technical design\n  and implementation plans before coding.\n[Pass]: User manually sign-off verify.md\n  checkbox, blocking next coding stages.",
