    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "r2c2_text",
      "x": 320,
      "y": 360,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "• 2.1 TDD: Code & tests (unit/integration/E2E)\n  must be delivered together (R-G-R loop)\n• 2.2 Atomic Commits: Small steps commits\n• 2.3 Valid Mocking: Verify assertions carefully;\n  prevent dummy mocks/false-positive passes",
      "originalText": "• 2.1 TDD: Code & tests (unit/integration/E2E)\n  must be delivered together (R-G-R loop)\n• 2.2 Atomic Commits: Small steps commits\n• 2.3 Valid Mocking: Verify assertions carefully;\n  prevent dummy mocks/false-positive passes",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
