      "y": 360,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "🛑 Gate B: CI & Code Review Gate\n\n[Audit]:\n1. CI: Auto-run full test suites & coverage.\n2. Peer Review: Review code changes.\n[Pass]: CI green & >= 1 RD Approve. No bypass.",
